r treatments instead of drop shadows. Surfaces move from Obsidian base to Layer 1 and Layer 2."}, {"id": "hyusecs_github_io_product", "label": "Product Manifesto", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "PRODUCT.md"}, {"id": "concept_high_craft", "label": "High-Craft Design", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "PRODUCT.md", "rationale": "Obsessive attention to detail in animations, telemetry data, and system-level status."}, {"id": "concept_show_dont_tell", "label": "Show, Don't Tell Principle", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "PRODUCT.md", "rationale": "Use live telemetry and working code patterns (typewriters, terminal logs) to prove expertise rather than static claims."}, {"id": "concept_the_machine_aesthetic", "label": "The Machine Aesthetic", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "PRODUCT.md", "rationale": "Embrace the raw materials of computing—grids, terminal prompts, and status daemons."}, {"id": "public_legaspi_resume_pdf", "label": "LEGASPI_RESUME.pdf", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "/home/hyuse/Desktop/hyusecs.github.io/public/LEGASPI_RESUME.pdf"}, {"id": "public_favicon_svg", "label": "Favicon", "file_type": "image", "source_file": "public/favicon.svg"}, {"id": "assets_astro_svg", "label": "Astro Logo", "file_type": "image", "source_file": "src/assets/astro.svg"}, {"id": "assets_background_svg", "label": "Background Graphic", "file_type": "image", "source_file": "src/assets/background.svg"}], "edges": [{"source": "scratch_code", "target": "components_telemetry_telemetry", "relation": "semantically_similar_to", "confidence": "INFERRED", "confidence_score": 0.85, "source_file": "scratch.js"}, {"source": "components_contact_astro", "target": "firebase_config_ts_getsystemconfig", "relation": "calls", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1, "source_file": "/home/hyuse/Desktop/hyusecs.github.io/src/components/Contact.astro"}, {"source": "components_contact_astro", "target": "public_legaspi_resume_pdf", "relation": "refere